{"tid":684970,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"「模型」求救，關節上唔到色","createTime":"2018-05-31T04:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T08:54:04.000Z","uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"46d7522c4e0017d5307d60a98919c7392f35d5d2","tid":684970,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:27:56.000Z","msg":"話說最近砌隻hg sf revive , 想幫啲關節上返金色（本身屎黃色），但唔知點解用乜方法都上唔到色，第一次噴咗黑補土再上金色（用郡氏金色噴罐），但後尾係撚咁甩啲金粉，甩到成手都係，最後發黑痴撚線，之後買多份關節parts 重新上，用筆塗但漆膜太厚，會同前臂零件磨甩色，仲有咩方法可以同關節上返啲金色？定要硬食啲屎黃色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/122706_239aeffd3bd224d8aadb920fa4925a0a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F122706_239aeffd3bd224d8aadb920fa4925a0a.png&h=f5dd247a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/122721_b8f6c4c7dba7d02070dd8c226a35b479.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F122721_b8f6c4c7dba7d02070dd8c226a35b479.png&h=109cb2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家暫時筆塗咗啲金色，但係都開始發黑，唔知做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca65445a53d092a39f74f16f81c34e0e5cd2305","tid":684970,"uid":57835,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"Freedom靚好多"},{"pid":"f299aec0709f312b2a45eefbd2d8d2f3a9a78cbf","tid":684970,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fca65445a53d092a39f74f16f81c34e0e5cd2305","tid":684970,"uid":57835,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"Freedom靚好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T06:39:24.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4ce285f0d9baeb46836c3c631557fdbcf58e54","tid":68